{"id": 1581, "genre": 1000, "title": "这年头，哪些东西消失了你也很难注意到？", "description": "这世界不仅信息量过大，还经常一天一个样。（题图来自：林小妖）", "record_count": 30594, "comment_count": 45, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20170322142317e3unj0aTBvWDPztx.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 1, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2017-03-22T17:00:09Z", "questions": [{"id": 2050, "title": "这年头，哪些东西消失了你也很难注意到？", "content": "这年头，哪些东西消失了你也很难注意到？", "genre": 2, "options": [{"id": 182030, "content": "订阅从不看的一个公众号再也不更新了，半年之后才想起来去找", "image": "img/option/option/20170321153044fPG78NJHLcsXIbBV.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 182031, "content": "家附近一个店关门重新装修，死活想不起来它原来是什么", "image": "img/option/option/20170321153424GgotEa2uNqwV9Oxl.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 182032, "content": "好几家O2O停止服务，拿的优惠券过期了也注意不到", "image": "img/option/option/20170321153859auRLgFMmzJ2tQZ0q.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 182034, "content": "突然心血来潮想去买本大学时候经常看的杂志，书报亭说老早停刊了", "image": "img/option/option/20170321154805TqzJlG0OUdNjR5F3.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 182035, "content": "手机支付用多了以至于钱包丢了也要很久之后才发现", "image": "img/option/option/20170321155450wELOtoaTMZKWph2q.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 182038, "content": "各种电商购物车里的东西太多，总有很多默默地失效了", "image": "img/option/option/20170321161738BAS9QUXE2hubwPOn.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 182041, "content": "微博、豆瓣、知乎上的收藏早就被发布者删掉了也全然不知", "image": "img/option/option/20170321161129kABKbdRTm4wYsfqP.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 182047, "content": "知道但不太关注的明星，有的组合解散三年了我也不知道", "image": "img/option/option/20170321162239DNyWY4jP9g0CfOMR.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}]}]}